missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/mission-context.md:833:First, it has the strongest novelty ceiling. If it works positively at all, it does not merely rank obstructions or repackage tensor structure; it produces a theorem-like compactness-rigidity program with one host space, one critical object, one contradiction mechanism, and one sharply identified missing lemma. That is the highest-upside presentable output in the field.
missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/mission-context.md:835:Second, its floor is still strong after refinement. The branch now forces an extraction-package audit before any rigidity rhetoric, defines the critical element before choosing a rigidity mechanism, and allows a precise obstruction result if the route dies at extraction, formulation, definability, coercivity, or contradiction. That makes failure informative rather than aesthetic.
